Package net.sf.jguiraffe.gui.builder.impl

Class TestJellyBeanBuilder

  • java.lang.Object
    • net.sf.jguiraffe.gui.builder.impl.TestJellyBeanBuilder
  • public class TestJellyBeanBuilder
extends Object
    Test class for JellyBeanBuilder. This class also tests the corresponding factory implementation. By executing a complex script with bean definitions the tag handler classes are also tested.
    Version:
    $Id: TestJellyBeanBuilder.java 207 2012-02-09 07:30:13Z oheger $
    Author:
    Oliver Heger
